      <title>壳牌因特朗普想要“关闭”的风电场损失 10 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/shell-takes-1-billion-hit-on-wind-farm-that-trump-wants-dead</link>
      <description><![CDATA[壳牌公司表示，由于总统唐纳德·特朗普试图通过行政命令阻碍该行业的发展，该公司已注销近 10 亿美元并退出美国海上风电场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/shell-takes-1-billion-hit-on-wind-farm-that-trump-wants-dead</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Jan 2025 10:42:26 GMT</pubDate>
